      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in absolute mint condition\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, pampered, and looks just as gorgeous as the day it was first bought. Not a single scratch or dent to be found! It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh car feel. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I know you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
