      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 in collector condition. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering razor-sharp response via its individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis is structurally flawless with documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension utilizing Bilstein dampers. Recent comprehensive service includes a full VANOS overhaul and precision valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates at peak performance. This is an uncompromised, analog driver\u2019s car with absolute mechanical integrity and zero parasitic power loss.",
