      "description": "Presenting a truly showroom-quality vehicle that serves as a benchmark for the model. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is in a time-capsule state; the premium leather remains supple without any creasing or bolster wear, and the original carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intricate driver-assist technologies, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive binder of service records showing all maintenance performed ahead of schedule at authorized centers. With low mileage and a history of adult ownership, this car offers a 'new-car' driving experience for the most discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
